Version: 0.6.0
Date: 2025-09-25

Current Task: Plan Core Reporting Module
Phase: 1 (Planning)

Goal: Design the foundational structure and UI for a new "Reporting" panel. This will serve as the home for all generated reports, such as the Annual Cost Analysis and Overage Utilization Report.

Key Objectives (this phase):

Define the layout of the new Reporting panel.

Scope the necessary UI controls for report generation (e.g., date range selectors, customer filters).

Create a placeholder for the new panel in the main navigation menu.

